snippet.title: Guitar Star | [ ALL SONGS ] Pathetic Plug and Play Guitar Hero knock off..
snippet.description:
This game blows and I hate this game and I subject myself to this shit. So this game is a rip off of Guitar Hero.. it's a plug and play console from I would say round 2004-2005 since it looks a lot like Guitar Hero  2. Not only the charts don't match any of the songs being played it also fails to do about anything right becuase once in a blue full moon you can hit a note.. rarely..

Too lazy to skip through? Well your in luck here are the time stamps

 - timestamps - 
00:00 - start & Warning
0:17 - Dream Police.
3:39  - I want you to want me 
6:42 - America
10:10 - I don't want to miss a thing
14:22 - YMCA 
17:45 - Highway star
22:12 - Thriller (No not that thriller your thinking about) 
28:06 - Darthy Started  (It's actually Party Started but oh noo they didn't want to get sued.) 
30:49 - Girl in the band (Thank god my pain is now done since there are no more songs..)
